<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>235</hymn_number>
<key>C</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Aa hung ciami hauka chungin, Vailam-tah ceunak a ra, Jesuh dawtnak ni
 ceu bangin, Kannih sinah a lang cang.

[C1]
   Jesuh dawtnak a tam bik ca, Khi hauka cu keimah luhnak, Keimah caah,
   Kei ca an hun cia cang.

[V2]
 Khamhnak kha a duhmi vialte, Hi hauka mi dihlak ca, Chaw ngei, ngei
 lo, a lian, a hme, Mi phunkip an zapi ca.

[C2]
   Jesuh dawtnak a tam bik ca, Khi hauka cu keimah luhnak, Keimah caah,
   Kei ca an hun cia cang.

[V3]
 Thinphang le aw-lok-chongmi ca, Zaangfahnak kaa a hun ko,
 Vailam-tahnak nan put caah, Nunnak laksawng nan hmuh lai.

[C3]
   Jesuh dawtnak a tam bik ca, Khi hauka cu keimah luhnak, Keimah caah,
   Kei ca an hun cia cang.

[V4]
 Mah hin kan put vailamtahnak, Thihnak ral ah kan chiah lai, Nunnak
 laksawng kan i lak i, Jesuh kha kan dawt chin lai.

[C4]
   Jesuh dawtnak a tam bik ca, Khi hauka cu keimah luhnak, Keimah caah,
   Kei ca an hun cia cang.</lyrics>
<title>AA HUNG CIAMI HAUKA CH235</title>
</song>